{"tid":1980624,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"我發覺著親動漫tee出街既人，多數都唔似正常人....","createTime":"2020-04-20T08:08:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T04:23:46.000Z","uid":75100,"like":8,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"78c32fde527fa8e5d4571cca68ebed94ddf38873","tid":1980624,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T08:08:07.000Z","msg":"呢2日已經見到3個，全部污污槽槽咁，隔住10m都感受到佢浸毒氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有2個係留長頭髮，又扎哂馬尾咁，係咪以為自己會好似佐佐木小次郎咁瀟灑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第1個著LL，件衫類似下圖啦，哇屌真係想像唔到有人敢咁著出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個陣咁岩7-11我排佢後面，屌佢望落都23-24碎，八達通居然夠薑增值$50!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後增值完比錢個陣，隔住銀包拍唔到，條友即刻勁高音懶chok咁: 「咦點解拍唔到架!喂喂喂」，然後攞左張八達通出黎，哇屌佢仲要2面痴哂D LL貼紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚇到我即刻退後幾步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqVQM7H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqVQM7H.png&h=c57ce3ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第2個就著刀劍神域，exact7ly係下圖個件，本身見佢識欣賞刀劍，應該係正常人，但原來我錯了.....佢係我對面馬路，行過黎個陣係超級自信 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似係行catwalk咁，每一步都feel到佢對SAO既愛，好自豪自己可以著公廁娜桐狗係身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢d著動漫tee既人，其實係咪好想多d人見到佢/ 成為注目點??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dMGP2Kd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdMGP2Kd.png&h=1fd6afe4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa06627b5b14cfe6bc4967fe23828b72d82d311a","tid":1980624,"uid":79793,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T08:09:42.000Z","msg":"好撚嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass